fields.heading: Application Process
fields.description: The process of application is done by us with utmost care and perfection. We undergo every instructions and guidelines provided by the Colleges universities carefully. We take special care in filling the application details and initials in order to avoid mistakes. All you need to do is to provide all the relevant details in the correct data and information.

fields.heading: Proper Assistance
fields.description: We consider that it is our core duty to assist you in the whole process. Thus, we provide all the relevant help required during the entire procedure such as arrival, departure, Visa, travel, scholarship, accommodation, etc. You can knock us anytime whenever you feel any difficulty in the process, we are there to guide and instruct you.

fields.heading: Perfect Counselling
fields.description: With us, you will get the right path to your dreams. Among the list of multiple options, we help you to choose the perfect one for yourself matching your preferences and meeting your parameters such as budget, aptitude, ability, field of interest, etc. We also provide you guidance regarding finance like loans and insurances.

fields.heading: Accurate Information
fields.description: We believe in perfection and invest our time in collecting all the information perfectly. We use the right resources to get the correct and accurate information regarding the different universities— its environment, eligibility criteria, qualifications, application process, admission requirements, arrival procedures and many more.

fields.heading: Career Planning
fields.description: As you finish your MBBS course, we guide you ahead for further studies. You can consult our experienced mentors regarding post-graduation courses, and they will help you with apt solutions.

fields.heading: Financial Advice
fields.description: Studying abroad sounds nice until parents face a financial crisis. So we are here to help you manage all the tuition fees, from food expenses to air tickets. So contact Eklavya and do not compromise your dreams.

fields.heading: Visa and Admission
fields.description: Studying abroad requires you to get a visa. At Eklavya, we assist you with the course details and guide you to apply for a visa and prepare the related documents.

fields.heading: Accommodations
fields.description: Not surprisingly, travel and accommodations are two significant concerns when studying abroad. If you contact us, we will help you book flight tickets, find suitable accommodations near the university.

Pursuing an MBBS degree in Georgia has gained popularity among international students due to its English-taught programs, affordability, and quality education. Georgian medical universities offer comprehensive courses in English, making it convenient for students from around the world. The tuition fees are budget-friendly compared to Western countries, and the overall cost of living is reasonable. Renowned for their high educational standards, these universities provide modern facilities and well-equipped laboratories. The degrees obtained are internationally recognized, enabling graduates to practice medicine globally. With a diverse student community, practical training in real medical settings, and a duration of around 6 years, studying MBBS in Georgia opens doors to a promising medical career.

Certification studying in Georgia offers a valuable avenue for individuals seeking specialized expertise and skill enhancement in various fields. These focused programs are tailored to provide targeted knowledge and practical skills, without the commitment of a full degree. From professional certifications that validate industry-specific skills in areas like IT and finance to language certifications that enhance communication abilities, Georgia's diverse range of certification programs caters to a broad spectrum of interests. Technical certifications in coding, digital marketing, and project management equip individuals with practical know-how crucial in today's job market. Moreover, certifications in healthcare, creative arts, education, data science, and environmental practices ensure that learners can align their education with their career goals, making certification studying a dynamic and effective approach to career advancement.

Georgia's diverse educational landscape offers a multitude of courses spanning various disciplines. Renowned for its medical programs, the country provides opportunities in fields like medicine, dentistry, and pharmacy. Engineering courses, including mechanical, electrical, and computer engineering, cater to the tech-savvy. Business and management programs cover administration, finance, and marketing. Computer science and information technology courses address the digital age's demands. Georgia's thriving tourism sector drives courses in hospitality and tourism management. Social sciences encompass psychology, sociology, and political science, while natural sciences include biology and chemistry. Language studies, art and design, law, education, agriculture, and environmental sciences round out the comprehensive array of courses available, ensuring a well-rounded education for diverse academic interests.
